contentrichtext.text: {{wiktionary}} '''OMC''' may refer to: ==Organizations== * Olifant Manufacturing Company of South Africa, now known as [[Land Systems OMC]] * Organisation mondiale du commerce (French for [[World Trade Organization]]) * Organización Mundial del Comercio (Spanish for [[World Trade Organization]]) * Organização Mundial de Comércio (Portuguese for [[World Trade Organization]]) * [[Outboard Marine Corporation]] * [[Omnicom Group]] Inc. (stock symbol) * OMC is a leading manufacturing company for window covering products ([http://www.omcblinds.com www.omcblinds.com]) ==Places== * [[Ormoc Airport]] in Ormoc City, Leyte, the Philippines ==Musical groups== * [[OMC (band)]], a New Zealand music group formerly known as Otara Millionaires Club * [[Old Man's Child]], a Norwegian Black metal band ==Other== * [[octyl methoxycinnamate]], the active ingredient in sunscreens * [[Open Method of Coordination]], a means of governance in the European Union * [[Operations and Maintenance Centre]] * [[Ontario Medal for Good Citizenship]] {{disambiguation}}
